Paper: hep-th/0007009

Date: 2000-07-03

Title: Nondegenerate Super-Anti-de Sitter Algebra and a Superstring Action

Authors: Machiko Hatsuda, Kiyoshi Kamimura and Makoto Sakaguchi

Comments: Latex, 12 pages, explanations added, version to be published in Phys.

Rev. DJournal-ref: Phys.Rev. D62 (2000) 105024

We construct an Anti-de Sitter(AdS) algebra in a nondegenerate superspace.Based on this algebra we construct a covariant kappa-symmetric superstringGreen-Schwarz superstring action in flat limit, the auxiliary fermioniccoordinates of the nondegenerate superspace becomes dynamical in the AdSbackground.